<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currently, Zend_Pdf lacks ability to sign PDF documents using digital certificates.</p>

<p>I created a class that enhances Zend_Pdf by adding the functionality to attach digital certificates.
You can download it here: <a href="http://program.farit.ru/#certificate">http://program.farit.ru/#certificate</a></p>

<p>It's easy to incorporate the ability to add details information into the certificate signature.</p>

<p>There are a few limitations. It can't work with PDF documents that have AcroForm elements: already signed, with forms, etc.</p>

